headline: This High-Yield Dividend Stock Continues Its Wheeling and Dealing With $5.5 Billion of Additional Deals
summary: Oneok (NYSE: OKE) has been busy over the past couple of years.  The midstream giant has closed several acquisitions that significantly increased its scale, diversification, and growth profile.  The company recently unveiled two more deals to further enhance its scale and strengthen its financial profile.
